<p><span style="font-size:130%;">an·o·rak</span><br />
/ˈanəˌrak/<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<em>noun</em><br />
noun: anorak; plural noun: anoraks; alternative spellings: Anorrack, Annoraaq, A|\|0|2a|&lt;</p>
<p>1. a waterproof jacket, typically with a hood, of a kind originally used in polar regions.<br />
2. a studious or obsessive person with unfashionable and largely solitary interests.<br />
3. an extremely bad author, typically found on IRC and Discord, often procrastinating and putting off doing actual work.</p>
<p>Example: <em>&quot;Oh yeah, Anorrack, he's that one author that made these articles:&quot;</em></p>
